Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚倒在了正门口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  九澄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的杀人鬼少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的真面目居然是…栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  快回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就到上课时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后图书室见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？栉名田请假了吗  真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  身体又不舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这里总是拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里呀  像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想听香织姐姐的示范演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那份名单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你才把名单交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这镇子原本就不需要那些人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偏偏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  并不是指你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用在意  我只是打杂的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成工作了就立刻从这里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的事是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还需要去接麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些事想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想听听伯父的意见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于嫦娥狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神原本是本地人敬拜的土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说从前这一带生活着狼群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神化身成狼并守护着城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得之前和博士君的父亲说的…大神和嫦娥狼的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说山里还有嫦娥狼生存着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是大型野生动物能够悄然生存的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大神传说还流传着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥狼就会继续生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了这样的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我更觉得是恰好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过大神的信仰和传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩盖了至今仍生存着的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那嫦娥狼现在还存在着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但那也许和我们所想的狼是不同的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是传说以前生活在这一带的大型狼——嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是越是调查它的真相就越是模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能证明它存在过的证据太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  嫦娥镇以外的地方都不承认其存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个我个人的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许嫦娥狼和普通的狼是完全不同的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如是拥有人类般智慧的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为凶月  带来不幸的红色月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不吉利的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道彗星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样被当作不吉利的象征的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如传言中数年后将要到来的哈雷彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是不吉利的象征之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻它是会带来疾病的凶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那彗星一样被当作不吉利的象征的  就是凶月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天的气温和湿度都比以往要高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷热的天气持续到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特产的八朔也收获不济
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做各种调查的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了含有嫦娥狼和凶月这些关键词的「嫦娥数数歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超自然魂告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些歌词里一定隐藏着什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是常有的设定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  我现在打算去地方资料馆调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对了  如果找到嫦娥数数歌的歌词的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能听取下伯父的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会告诉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又偷懒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始学习不是挺认真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授都夸奖你很勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在却人不像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得地质学没意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃饭就得花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此必须要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你又是为了什么来到大学的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老在外面吃饭也不考虑下花费  还喊穷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做饭不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑脸我真的觉得很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来打个招呼多好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真没想到您还会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就这么觉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生的笑脸一定很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  刚才的音色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还远远不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想去东京的音大认真学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能离开这座城镇所以放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天来学习小提琴的学生烤了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起来品尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要为三重子复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人好像回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  麻奈做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？我为了香织姐姐努力做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我们就开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  我们已经在「中心」保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我想查一下「嫦娥数数歌」的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌啊  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌…  数数歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在里面的D13号书架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月盈盈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨镰下矣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「落神」的仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  麻奈她的话  已经被令尊接走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是刚好错过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才该道歉呢  来得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说谎  请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是在这里  一个女人拿着巨大的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你现在方便么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也见过杀人现场？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过那已经是四年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我也和你一样  想去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可警局却空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人现场也消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被杀的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新珠三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩在同一所大学读书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为了写毕业论文  而造访了这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却万万没有想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而至于当时那不知底细的杀人集团…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个杀人集团之中  拿着巨型镰刀的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们班上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田眠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这些话  反正也不会有人信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法向任何人谈起这事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我想  如果是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话  一定是能够相信我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我说…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贤木俊一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…  欢迎回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去香织小姐那儿去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果说她已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洋葱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  我能进来么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他好担…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐她说  从今天开始  不准备再教我拉小提琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐她…  没有说原因么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因为看到大姐姐她有时无精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想多陪陪她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  我也很担心香织小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆下回就不以上课的名义  而是去探望她如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人么？  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喊破喉咙也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那样么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那样」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你是不是也成了「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是你的恋人？  还是你喜欢的对象？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你的对象  也像摘花前辈那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花前辈  是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚大哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  非常喜欢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他能够给我一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我被送到了这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神人」是指什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你还没有听说么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  为人身  而又非人之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没窗子对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这里应该是地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下雨  排水沟中的流水声  就从天花板上传来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的那位摘花前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于戒律所定的「落神之式」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落神？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个说法  就是被处决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为「神人」的前辈  和我接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我便不再为人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人身  而非人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上现在  也对气味非常敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上  有着「神堕人」的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背律神人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回荡四野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒然之声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户目中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪泪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多的事  犹如风车一般转个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我  只是在不明所以地观望着这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  错综
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.31,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:29.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:43.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君にもう一人きりで待たないでと　言い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:49.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色あせてく　世界の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:55.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らは終りへ旅をする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:03:01.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その束の間に　君と出会った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命を削るように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:17.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の向こうに確かにあった　遥かな故郷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君とゆけるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.69,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:35.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜の向こうに　幻の空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:29.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:43.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口难开 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:49.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渐次斑驳  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:55.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至终焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:03:01.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之间  逢见君影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:17.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故乡迢迢  时之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:20.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.69,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无爱无心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:35.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻苍空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,


